OL,3,CWoman's wait for heart transplant
OL,4,Ccould take 'many more years'
OL,6,FITV News' Louisa Britton has been
OL,7,Fspeaking to Kerry Fear from Yeovil,
OL,8,Fwho has been on the organ donation
OL,9,Fwaiting list for more than a year.
OL,11,FA woman from Somerset who has been
OL,12,Fliving with a heart condition for
OL,13,Fdecades has said she could have to
OL,14,Fwait "many more years" for a life-
OL,15,Fsaving transplant.
OL,17,FKerry Fear, from Yeovil, has been on
OL,18,Fthe organ donation waiting list for
OL,19,Fmore than 12 months already, after
OL,20,Fdoctors told her her heart was
OL,21,F"failing."
