OL,3,CWoman's wait for heart transplant
OL,4,Ccould take 'many more years'
OL,6,FThe 50-year-old, who was born with two
OL,7,Fholes in her heart, two of her
OL,8,Farteries the wrong way round, and only
OL,9,Fthree heart chambers, has had multiple
OL,10,Fheart surgeries and pacemakers fitted
OL,11,Fthroughout her life to manage her
OL,12,Fcomplex heart condition.
OL,14,FBut she said the treatments are
OL,15,Fbecoming less effective, and she was
OL,16,Fadded to the waiting list for a heart
OL,17,Ftransplant in May 2024.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
