OL,3,CWoman's wait for heart transplant
OL,4,Ccould take 'many more years'
OL,6,FMs Fear said: "I've noticed that my
OL,7,Fheart rhythm isn't normal and has been
OL,8,Fslowly declining. I don't feel
OL,9,Fbrilliant. I don't feel terrible. But
OL,10,Fyou can deteriorate quickly.
OL,12,F"I knew being listed for a transplant
OL,13,Fwas coming. At first, it was scary as
OL,14,Fyou realise the magnitude of it. But
OL,15,Fas time goes on, you have to get on
OL,16,Fwith life."
