OL,3,CWoman's wait for heart transplant
OL,4,Ccould take 'many more years'
OL,6,FThe NHS has warned it's facing an
OL,7,F"incredibly concerning situation"
OL,8,Fwhere more people than ever are
OL,9,Fwaiting for transplants, but fewer
OL,10,Fdonations are taking place.
OL,12,FFigures from NHS Blood and Transplant
OL,13,Fshow donor show 8,096 patients in the
OL,14,FUK were on the active transplant
OL,15,Fwaiting list as of 31 March 2025 ` the
OL,16,Fhighest number on record.
OL,18,FIn the South West, 596 people are
OL,19,Fcurrently on the waiting list for a
OL,20,Ftransplant.
