OL,3,CWoman's wait for heart transplant
OL,4,Ccould take 'many more years'
OL,6,FUnder the 'opt-out' system, donation
OL,7,Fcan only go ahead with the family's
OL,8,Fsupport and consent rates for organ
OL,9,Fdonation across the UK are at 59%.
OL,11,FDirector of Organ and Tissue Donation
OL,12,Fand Transplantation, Anthony Clarkson,
OL,13,Fhas urged people to take action by
OL,14,Fregistering their decision on the NHS
OL,15,FOrgan Donor Register.
