OL,3,CWoman's wait for heart transplant
OL,4,Ccould take 'many more years'
OL,6,FMs Fear said a transplant would give
OL,7,Fher "confidence and freedom," but she
OL,8,Fis determined to enjoy life as much as
OL,9,Fshe can while she is on the waiting
OL,10,Flist.
OL,12,F"I don't want to miss anything or
OL,13,Fwaste any time when I can do what I
OL,14,Fcan at the moment.
OL,16,F"Most days, I put waiting to the back
OL,17,Fof my mind. If I think about it, it's
OL,18,Fquite an odd thing ` it could happen
OL,19,Fany time, and I am used to surgery,
OL,20,Fbut this is very different.
